{"tid":748794,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌奶星 m記個shark shark 薯條簡直係垃圾","createTime":"2018-07-19T13:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T10:09:53.000Z","uid":70029,"like":16,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4c87cd766ed204a5a9a7eb3e53f42861be838550","tid":748794,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:09:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的 近排m記又出返shark shark 薯條<br />\n咁我上個禮拜去食bbq味啦 屌奶星點知shark完之後 完全唔覺得有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁我以為係呢批課既問題啦 <br />\n<br />\n點知岩岩又走去另一間m記食 今次食紫菜味 屌奶星 又係冇味 真係拎包鹽/pepper去shake都好味過d垃圾粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條女仲要叫我買外賣比佢 屌 包粉留返黎茶係我碌鳩上面比佢含當玩下花式算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不知所謂"},{"pid":"c0aa8536cccf40a3c2571717ccbbf7410495551b","tid":748794,"uid":49974,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"shake shake賓周，你條女真識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879cf92f743a169130cb6a3148c21b6d393f64e3","tid":748794,"uid":124824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:31:48.000Z","msg":"你應該買泡菜味<br />\n再倒落佢個閪到奶"},{"pid":"852d65f9bae70b39d95eb49d7470af50e9a807d3","tid":748794,"uid":85057,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:33:26.000Z","msg":"Shark shark 薯條我都未食過"},{"pid":"4c8d36a72518be58500d761c47edbe196e92eb7d","tid":748794,"uid":66997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T14:00:43.000Z","msg":"樓主有病？好撚鹹喎"},{"pid":"8111bd6b2f1428c3e6ea78a18b4520e65c2bd273","tid":748794,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"879cf92f743a169130cb6a3148c21b6d393f64e3